# Empty States

Empty states guide users when there's no data to display.

## When to Use

- First-time user experience (no data yet)
- Search/filter returns no results
- List is empty after deletion
- No items match current filters

## Canonical component

Use the shared `EmptyState` molecule at `apps/web/src/components/molecules/EmptyState.tsx`.

```tsx
import { EmptyState } from '@/components/molecules/EmptyState';

<EmptyState
  scene="noVariants"
  title="No variants yet"
  description="Generate platform variants from your published content."
  actionLabel="Generate variants"
  onAction={handleGenerate}
/>
```

### Props

| Prop | Notes |
|------|-------|
| `scene` | Inline SVG illustration id ‚Äî preferred for Content Pipeline and other polished surfaces |
| `icon` | Lucide icon fallback when no `scene` is set |
| `title` / `description` | Required copy; keep brief and actionable |
| `actionLabel` / `onAction` | Primary CTA |
| `secondaryActionLabel` / `onSecondaryAction` | Optional secondary CTA |
| `variant` | `'default'` (elevated) or `'onboarding'` (step cards + pro tips) |

### Content Pipeline scene keys

| Scene | Use when |
|-------|----------|
| `actionRequired` | Missing both source content and brand profile |
| `noSource` | No PUBLISHED/PIPELINED workbench content |
| `noProfile` | No active Brand Identity profile |
| `noVariants` | Generated variants list is empty |
| `filteredEmpty` | Pillar or variant filters hide all items |
| `queueEmpty` | Publish Queue has no scheduled items |

Scenes live in `apps/web/src/components/molecules/empty-state/EmptyStateScenes.tsx`.

## Context-specific patterns

### No filter results

```tsx
<EmptyState
  scene="filteredEmpty"
  title="No variants match"
  description="Try adjusting platform, date, or status filters."
  actionLabel="Clear filters"
  onAction={clearFilters}
/>
```

### First-time user (icon fallback)

```tsx
import { Sparkles } from 'lucide-react';

<EmptyState
  icon={Sparkles}
  title="Welcome to Tasks!"
  description="Create your first task to start organizing your work."
  actionLabel="Create Your First Task"
  onAction={onCreate}
/>
```

## Best Practices

1. **Be helpful** ‚Äî explain why it's empty and what to do next
2. **Provide action** ‚Äî include a clear next step when possible
3. **Prefer `scene` in Personal Branding** ‚Äî illustrated empty states match the product polish bar
4. **Keep it brief** ‚Äî short title, 1‚Äì2 sentence description
5. **Stay positive** ‚Äî encouraging tone, not error-like
6. **Consider context** ‚Äî first-time vs filtered vs completed
